title: John Porcell from Youth of Today/Shelter/Judge
itunes:title: John Porcell from Youth of Today/Shelter/Judge
description:
Episode 266 - Happy Wednesday! Today we have hardcore hero, John Porcell on the show. He’s played in every band ever included Youth of Today, Shelter, Judge, Project X and many more. Not only is he extremely musically talented, he’s a great dude to boot. We hung at his apartment one afternoon and discussed his early upbringing, life on a farm and ego. It’s a wide ranging discussion that I am very happy to share with you! Use our Amazon Affiliate Code to support the show!
